column2: SELECT s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subClass, s.sciencePrimary,   s.survey, s.programname, s.legacy_target1, s.boss_target1,   s.eboss_target0,  p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.bestObjID,  g.dered_u, g.dered_g, g.dered_r, g.dered_i, g.dered_z FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID = p.objID WHERE s.ra BETWEEN # and #  AND s.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND s.class = &&&  AND (legacy_target1 & (# | # | #)) > #  AND s.z BETWEEN # and #  AND s.zWarning = # ORDER BY s.z
